node.text:
We did it for the kids!! 👊 

Hope you raise tons of money for all the kids 
 at @bostonchildrens this year @granitetelecom, glad to be a part of it. 

Thank you Vinny and Ralphie for donating your time and hair/fur. 

And don’t worry folks, I used a brand new manscaper on Vinny 🤣 @poparotc 

#savingbyshaving #doitforthekids

node.text:
A little while ago, I got to surprise Ethan with a video call. Ethan is a young football fan, a Burkitt #lymphoma survivor, and one of the strongest kids! Thank you LLS for including me in the Light The Night #RandomActsOfLight movement and for celebrating kids like Ethan. 

Ethan, it was great to meet you, stay strong man!! To all the other kids and people fighting cancer, keep going, you got this!! 💪

Donate to help bring light to the darkness of cancer at LLS.org. #sponsored

node.text: What a dad! Thanks for keeping us 5 boys in line growing up and for being an incredible role model. From playing in the backyard, to building a gym in your basement to help us improve (and stay out of trouble!), to being the #1 fan at all our games, We’re lucky to have you @papagronk! HFD to the Creator!! #fathersday
